  "title": "야뇨(유뇨)의 한방치료  [사당동 남성역 이수한의원]",
  "addDate": "2011. 1. 17.",
  "categoryNo": "39",
  "parentCategoryNo": "9",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110101152023",
  "html_size": 180835,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110101152023\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110101152023\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt\"><strong><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20110117_164/isuhani_12952362759210usV4_JPEG/%BE%DF%B4%A2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"240\" height=\"168\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"20110117_164/isuhani_12952362759210usV4_JPEG/%BE%DF%B4%A2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A28A4117')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20110117_164/isuhani_12952362759210usV4_JPEG/%BE%DF%B4%A2.jpg?type=w3\"></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt\"><strong>소아야뇨(유뇨)는&nbsp;선천적으로&nbsp;신기(腎氣)가&nbsp;부족하거나&nbsp;체질이&nbsp;허약하여&nbsp;이로&nbsp;인해&nbsp;방광이&nbsp;차가워져서&nbsp;잘&nbsp;생깁니다.&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0000; FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">신장의 기운을 북돋아주면서 방광을 따뜻하게 해주는 한약 </span><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0000; FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">처방을&nbsp;사용하거나&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0000; FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">심리적&nbsp;원인으로&nbsp;인한&nbsp;경우에는&nbsp;스트레스를 해소하고&nbsp;신기(神</span><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0000; FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">氣)를 다스려 마음을 편안하게 해주는 한약 처방을</span><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0000; FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">&nbsp;사용할&nbsp;수&nbsp;있습니다.&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">평소에&nbsp;오미자(五味子)나&nbsp;산수유(山茱萸)</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">등을&nbsp;</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">먹이면&nbsp;도움이&nbsp;됩니다.</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt\"><strong>야뇨(유뇨)를&nbsp;치료함에&nbsp;있어&nbsp;벌을&nbsp;주는&nbsp;것은&nbsp;좋지&nbsp;않으며&nbsp;먼저&nbsp;환아의&nbsp;협조를&nbsp;구하도록&nbsp;하고,&nbsp;치료에&nbsp;대한&nbsp;반응을&nbsp;알&nbsp;수&nbsp;있도록&nbsp;배뇨일지를&nbsp;작성하는&nbsp;것도&nbsp;좋은&nbsp;방법입니다.&nbsp;가능한&nbsp;취침&nbsp;전에&nbsp;소변을&nbsp;보게&nbsp;하는&nbsp;것이&nbsp;필요하며,&nbsp;또한&nbsp;낮에&nbsp;소변을&nbsp;보고자&nbsp;할&nbsp;때&nbsp;단계적으로&nbsp;참는&nbsp;훈련을&nbsp;실시하여&nbsp;방광의&nbsp;용적을&nbsp;늘이고&nbsp;자율신경을&nbsp;단련시키는&nbsp;것도&nbsp;좋습니다.&nbsp;</strong></span><br /><br /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20110117_209/isuhani_1295236223587kQvOC_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"193\" height=\"48\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"20110117_209/isuhani_1295236223587kQvOC_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A28A4117')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20110117_209/isuhani_1295236223587kQvOC_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
